Paper: hep-th/9803084

Date: 1998-03-10

Title: Singular instantons and creation of open universes

Comments: 4 pages, revtex. Note added commenting on Hawking and Turok's

(hep-th/9803156) response to this paperJournal-ref: Phys.Rev. D57 (1998) 7069-7070

Singular instantons of the type introduced by Hawking and Turok(hep-th/9802030) lead to unacceptable physical consequences and cannot,therefore, be used to describe the creation of open universes.